  "body": "Hi all,\r\n\r\nWhen the beacon node begins, it needs to read the logs from a validator registration contract for registered validators.  When a validator deposits 32ETH into the contract on the mainchain, they pass in the public key they will be using for signing. This same public key will be used in the beacon node.\r\n\r\nTo do this, we should pass in the address of a deployed Validator Registration Contract as a CLI argument to the beacon node entry point, which will then use web3 to read logs from that address at a mainchain endpoint.",
